ark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="28">Great. Your valid UPI ID is:</p>
<p data-start="30" data-end="50"><strong data-start="30" data-end="50"><code data-start="32" data-end="48">7099805039@ybl</code></strong></p>
<p data-start="52" data-end="99">I've generated a new QR code using this UPI ID.</p>
<p data-start="101" data-end="218"><strong data-start="101" data-end="122">Download it here:</strong><br>
<span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button"><strong data-start="124" data-end="164">📱 PhonePe_UPI_QR_7099805039_ybl.png</strong></button></span></p>
<p data-start="220" data-end="290">If this QR still doesn't work, then the issue is usually one of these:</p>
<ul data-start="292" data-end="450">
<li data-section-id="xjuhn9" data-start="292" data-end="323">
<p data-start="294" data-end="323">The UPI ID is not active yet.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mthhvq" data-start="324" data-end="349">
<p data-start="326" data-end="349">The UPI ID has changed.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dkq34d" data-start="350" data-end="393">
<p data-start="352" data-end="393">The linked bank account has been removed.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1r12418" data-start="394" data-end="450">
<p data-start="396" data-end="450">The PhonePe account isn't enabled to receive payments.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="452" data-end="757">You can verify it by opening any UPI app (PhonePe, Google Pay, BHIM, or Paytm) and trying to send <strong data-start="550" data-end="556">₹1</strong> to <strong data-start="560" data-end="580"><code data-start="562" data-end="578">7099805039@ybl</code></strong>. If the app shows your name (<strong data-start="610" data-end="627">ANANDA SARMAH</strong>) before payment, the UPI ID is valid. If it says <strong data-start="677" data-end="699">"UPI ID not found"</strong> or <strong data-start="703" data-end="720">"Invalid VPA"</strong>, then the UPI ID itself is inactive.</p>
<p data-start="759" data-end="828">If you're building <strong data-start="778" data-end="806">Numero Annand AI Premium</strong>, I can also generate:</p>
<ul data-start="829" data-end="994" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="11udheh" data-start="829" data-end="869">
<p data-start="831" data-end="869"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">a branded payment QR with your logo</span></span>,</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e8tlh5" data-start="870" data-end="910">
<p data-start="872" data-end="910"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">a fixed amount QR (e.g. ₹499, ₹999, ₹1999)</span></span>,</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="io0iyj" data-start="911" data-end="994" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="913" data-end="994" data-is-last-node="">or <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">a QR that automatically fills in the payment note (e.g. "Numero Annand AI Premium Purchase")</span></span>. <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Coding Citation" class="rounded-xl px-1 text-token-text-secondary bg-token-bg-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-interactive-bg-secondary-selected"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></p>
</li>
