text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">Stopped thinking<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="66822577-1bac-4f87-8840-df7d3c15a34e" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="41">I checked the QR code in your screenshot.</p>
<p data-start="43" data-end="89">The QR <strong data-start="50" data-end="75">does decode correctly</strong>. It contains:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="91" data-end="147"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl&amp;pn=Ananda Sarmah</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="149" data-end="187">So the image itself is <strong data-start="172" data-end="186">not broken</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="189" data-end="307">If scanning it says <strong data-start="209" data-end="225">"Invalid QR"</strong> or <strong data-start="229" data-end="260">"Couldn't complete payment"</strong>, the problem is almost certainly one of these:</p>
<ol data-start="309" data-end="457">
<li data-section-id="yiw15a" data-start="309" data-end="357">
<p data-start="312" data-end="357"><strong data-start="312" data-end="357"><code data-start="314" data-end="330">7099805039@ybl</code> is not an active UPI ID.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cccxr" data-start="358" data-end="419">
<p data-start="361" data-end="419">The UPI ID exists but is <strong data-start="386" data-end="418">not linked to a bank account</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1c53sjc" data-start="420" data-end="457">
<p data-start="423" data-end="457">The UPI ID has changed in PhonePe.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="1693gao" data-start="459" data-end="486">Let's verify the UPI ID</h3>
<p data-start="488" data-end="505">Open <strong data-start="493" data-end="504">PhonePe</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="507" data-end="612">
<li data-section-id="1qkfoux" data-start="507" data-end="526">
<p data-start="509" data-end="526">Tap your profile.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p0iegn" data-start="527" data-end="551">
<p data-start="529" data-end="551">Tap <strong data-start="533" data-end="550">Bank Accounts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nz4qv0" data-start="552" data-end="582">
<p data-start="554" data-end="582">Tap the linked bank account.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i01wnq" data-start="583" data-end="612">
<p data-start="585" data-end="612">Look at your <strong data-start="598" data-end="611">UPI ID(s)</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="614" data-end="661">Tell me <strong data-start="622" data-end="633">exactly</strong> what is shown, for example:</p>
<ul data-start="663" data-end="736">
<li data-section-id="aeb8n3" data-start="663" data-end="681">
<p data-start="665" data-end="681"><code data-start="665" data-end="681">7099805039@ybl</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="adywz3" data-start="682" data-end="700">
<p data-start="684" data-end="700"><code data-start="684" data-end="700">7099805039@ibl</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ae5b3x" data-start="701" data-end="719">
<p data-start="703" data-end="719"><code data-start="703" data-end="719">7099805039@axl</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="y9fg1r" data-start="720" data-end="736">
<p data-start="722" data-end="736">something else</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="19hggq9" data-start="738" data-end="754">An easy test</h3>
<p data-start="756" data-end="831">From any UPI app (PhonePe, Google Pay, BHIM, Paytm), try sending <strong data-start="821" data-end="827">₹1</strong> to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="833" data-end="859"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ybl</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="861" data-end="874">What happens?</p>
<ul data-start="876" data-end="1067">
<li data-section-id="f8lbra" data-start="876" data-end="957">
<p data-start="878" data-end="957">✅ It shows <strong data-start="889" data-end="906">Ananda Sarmah</strong> → the UPI ID is valid, and the issue is elsewhere.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uvn8fo" data-start="958" data-end="1067">
<p data-start="960" data-end="1067">❌ It says <strong data-start="970" data-end="990">UPI ID not found</strong> or <strong data-start="994" data-end="1009">Invalid VPA</strong> → the UPI ID is inactive, so every QR using it will fail.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1nozk0b" data-start="1069" data-end="1087">One more thing</h3>
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1279">Your website is hosted on Vercel. The QR shown there is <strong data-start="1145" data-end="1161">not the same</strong> as the full QR I generated earlier with the payment note. It appears your website is generating its own QR from code.</p>
<p data-start="1281" data-end="1368">Please paste the contents of the file that generates the QR. It is likely one of these:</p>
<ul data-start="1370" data-end="1411">
<li data-section-id="ys0oj" data-start="1370" data-end="1393">
<p data-start="1372" data-end="1393"><code data-start="1372" data-end="1393">upi_qr_generator.py</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="duewmt" data-start="1394" data-end="1411">
<p data-start="1396" data-end="1411"><code data-start="1396" data-end="1411">app/api/qr.py</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1511" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Once I see that code, I can tell you exactly why the website is generating a QR that doesn't work.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type=