<p data-start="1484" data-end="1532">PhonePe, GPay and Paytm will automatically fill:</p>
<ul data-start="1534" data-end="1632">
<li data-section-id="15xupo3" data-start="1534" data-end="1549">
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1549">Amount = ₹201</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mosrje" data-start="1550" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1552" data-end="1575">Receiver = Annand Sarma</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y4ynke" data-start="1576" data-end="1598">
<p data-start="1578" data-end="1598">UPI = 7099805039@ybl</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vhkk9e" data-start="1599" data-end="1632">
<p data-start="1601" data-end="1632">Note = Numero Annand AI Premium</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1634" data-end="1637">
<h2 data-section-id="1xvzrp" data-start="1639" data-end="1662">Step 6 (Recommended)</h2>
<p data-start="1664" data-end="1731">Instead of a fixed note, you can make it unique for every customer.</p>
<p data-start="1733" data-end="1745">For example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1747" data-end="1837"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">request</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>form[</span><span class="ͼz">"name"</span><span>]

</span><span class="ͼ11">note</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">f"Numero-</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼz">"</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼ11">generate_qr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼy">201</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">note</span><span>)</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1839" data-end="1893">If the customer enters <strong data-start="1862" data-end="1871">Rahul</strong>, the QR will contain:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1895" data-end="1921"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Note:
Numero-Rahul</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1923" data-end="1983">This makes it much easier to identify who made each payment.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="f383n" data-start="1985" data-end="2056"><span role="text">I can also give you a complete <code data-start="2020" data-end="2030">checkout</code> route that automatically:</span></h3>
<ul data-start="2057" data-end="2276" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="umybvi" data-start="2057" data-end="2082">
<p data-start="2059" data-end="2082">✅ takes the user's name</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mzltw4" data-start="2083" data-end="2128">
<p data-start="2085" data-end="2128">✅ takes the selected package (₹201 or ₹501)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bgc8iq" data-start="2129" data-end="2161">
<p data-start="2131" data-end="2161">✅ generates the QR dynamically</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="981nlz" data-start="2162" data-end="2202">
<p data-start="2164" data-end="2202">✅ fills the payment note automatically</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yarm3f" data-start="2203" data-end="2276" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="2205" data-end="2276" data-is-last-node="">✅ works with your current Flask project without any additional changes.</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" 