ing [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="37">Yes, the <strong data-start="9" data-end="36">filename is now correct</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="39" data-end="60">From your screenshot:</p>
<ul data-start="62" data-end="270">
<li data-section-id="vhtvil" data-start="62" data-end="90">
<p data-start="64" data-end="90">✅ Folder: <code data-start="74" data-end="90">static/images/</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zji4n" data-start="91" data-end="122">
<p data-start="93" data-end="122">✅ File name: <code data-start="106" data-end="122">payment_qr.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18p0fhk" data-start="123" data-end="186">
<p data-start="125" data-end="186">✅ GitHub is displaying it as an image (not HTML code anymore)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o6wnt0" data-start="187" data-end="270">
<p data-start="189" data-end="227">✅ The path matches what Flask expects:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="230" data-end="270"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>static/images/payment_qr.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="272" data-end="315">However, there is still one likely problem:</p>
<p data-start="317" data-end="453">The QR image itself may still contain <strong data-start="355" data-end="375">invalid UPI data</strong>. Simply renaming the file does not change what is encoded inside the QR code.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1wucrya" data-start="455" data-end="492">Check if the QR is actually valid</h3>
<p data-start="494" data-end="512">Scan the QR using:</p>
<ul data-start="513" data-end="568">
<li data-section-id="1cro7w5" data-start="513" data-end="526">
<p data-start="515" data-end="526">Google Lens</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tupqpt" data-start="527" data-end="536">
<p data-start="529" data-end="536">PhonePe</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1758509" data-start="537" data-end="544">
<p data-start="539" data-end="544">Paytm</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="69lgq4" data-start="545" data-end="568">
<p data-start="547" data-end="568">Any online QR decoder</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="570" data-end="623">If it is correct, it should decode to something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="625" data-end="730"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl&amp;pn=Annand%20Sarma&amp;am=201&amp;cu=INR&amp;tn=Numero%20Annand%20AI%20Premium</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="732" data-end="835">If it decodes to anything else (or doesn't decode at all), the QR image itself needs to be regenerated.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="lyxx8b" data-start="837" data-end="852">I recommend</h3>
<p data-start="854" data-end="981">Don't upload a QR image manually. Instead, generate it automatically from your Flask app using <code data-start="949" data-end="970">upi_qr_generator.py</code>. That way:</p>
<ul data-start="982" data-end="1169">
<li data-section-id="1rbgzy" data-start="982" data-end="1015">
<p data-start="984" data-end="1015">✅ The UPI ID is always correct.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="egvq6w" data-start="1016" data-end="1067">
<p data-start="1018" data-end="1067">✅ The amount updates automatically (₹201 / ₹501).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hub5xd" data-start="1068" data-end="1113">
<p data-start="1070" data-end="1113">✅ The payment note is filled automatically.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pys72u" data-start="1114" data-end="1169">
<p data-start="1116" data-end="1169">✅ You never have to replace the image manually again.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1171" data-end="1223">I can help you wire this into your existing project.</p>
<p data-start="1225" data-end="1286"><strong data-start="1225" data-end="1242">One question:</strong> when you scan the QR, what exactly happens?</p>
<ul data-start="1288" data-end="1465" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="x5olvb" data-start="1288" data-end="1329">
<p data-start="1290" data-end="1329">Does PhonePe say <strong data-start="1307" data-end="1328">"Invalid QR Code"</strong>?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="77g0zd" data-start="1330" data-end="1377">
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1377">Does it open but show <strong data-start="1354" data-end="1376">"No UPI app found"</strong>?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uluxei" data-start="1378" data-end="1419">
<p data-start="1380" data-end="1419">Does it open with the <strong data-start="1402" data-end="1418">wrong UPI ID</strong>?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vjicbk" data-start="1420" data-end="1465" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1422" data-end="1465" data-is-last-node="">Or does it show <strong data-start="1438" data-end="1464">₹0 and no payment note</strong>?</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" 