5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="38">I decoded the QR from your screenshot.</p>
<p data-start="40" data-end="64">The QR contains exactly:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="66" data-end="122"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl&amp;pn=Ananda Sarmah</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="zfunj7" data-start="124" data-end="143">What's missing?</h3>
<p data-start="145" data-end="167">Your QR only contains:</p>
<ul data-start="168" data-end="228">
<li data-section-id="vt0p9d" data-start="168" data-end="196">
<p data-start="170" data-end="196">✅ UPI ID: <code data-start="180" data-end="196">7099805039@ybl</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14g3omx" data-start="197" data-end="228">
<p data-start="199" data-end="228">✅ Payee Name: <code data-start="213" data-end="228">Ananda Sarmah</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="230" data-end="254">It does <strong data-start="238" data-end="245">not</strong> contain:</p>
<ul data-start="255" data-end="326">
<li data-section-id="vcjw7s" data-start="255" data-end="273">
<p data-start="257" data-end="273">❌ Amount (<code data-start="267" data-end="272">am=</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zsj0zg" data-start="274" data-end="297">
<p data-start="276" data-end="297">❌ Currency (<code data-start="288" data-end="296">cu=INR</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d5sq1i" data-start="298" data-end="326">
<p data-start="300" data-end="326">❌ Transaction Note (<code data-start="320" data-end="325">tn=</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="328" data-end="361">So it is just a <strong data-start="344" data-end="360">basic UPI QR</strong>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ts8y27" data-start="363" data-end="381">Is it invalid?</h3>
<p data-start="383" data-end="485">The decoded string is a valid UPI URI format. If PhonePe says <strong data-start="445" data-end="461">"Invalid QR"</strong>, the likely causes are:</p>
<ol data-start="487" data-end="705">
<li data-section-id="xxw4do" data-start="487" data-end="568">
<p data-start="490" data-end="568"><strong data-start="490" data-end="535">The UPI ID <code data-start="503" data-end="519">7099805039@ybl</code> is not active</strong> or not linked to a bank account.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mcvk58" data-start="569" data-end="612">
<p data-start="572" data-end="612">The UPI ID has been entered incorrectly.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vrq69v" data-start="613" data-end="705">
<p data-start="616" data-end="705">The UPI app/provider (<code data-start="638" data-end="644">@ybl</code>) is not recognizing that handle because it isn't registered.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="kdpu8w" data-start="707" data-end="727">Test your UPI ID</h3>
<p data-start="729" data-end="746">On another phone:</p>
<ol data-start="747" data-end="897">
<li data-section-id="a7o34l" data-start="747" data-end="777">
<p data-start="750" data-end="777">Open PhonePe or Google Pay.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="59hz6g" data-start="778" data-end="806">
<p data-start="781" data-end="806">Choose <strong data-start="788" data-end="805">Pay to UPI ID</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="k554jb" data-start="807" data-end="848">
<p data-start="810" data-end="816">Enter:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="820" data-end="848"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ybl</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-section-id="oye03x" data-start="849" data-end="897">
<p data-start="852" data-end="897">See if it shows your name and allows payment.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="899" data-end="1083">
<li data-section-id="10rcknb" data-start="899" data-end="984">
<p data-start="901" data-end="984">If it <strong data-start="907" data-end="934">doesn't find the UPI ID</strong>, the issue is with the UPI ID itself, not the QR.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11x0m07" data-start="985" data-end="1083">
<p data-start="987" data-end="1083">If it <strong data-start="993" data-end="1017">does find the UPI ID</strong>, then we can regenerate a richer QR with amount and payment note.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1106">Can you also tell me:</p>
<ul data-start="1107" data-end="1215" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="1jdnuxh" data-start="1107" data-end="1169">
<p data-start="1109" data-end="1169">Does entering <strong data-start="1123" data-end="1143"><code data-start="1125" data-end="1141">7099805039@ybl</code></strong> manually in PhonePe work?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="khg9h3" data-start="1170" data-end="1215" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1172" data-end="1215" data-is-last-node="">Or does PhonePe say <strong data-start="1192" data-end="1214">"UPI ID not found"</strong>?</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" 