x,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-13" data-turn-id-container="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-13" data-testid="conversation-turn-92" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c5dc4e0f-912a-4f91-9539-8787552ee136" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="141">Based on everything you've shown, here's the order I'd recommend. Don't change your code yet—the first step is to verify the payment details.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1q1czay" data-start="143" data-end="190">Step 1 (Most important): Verify your UPI ID</h3>
<p data-start="191" data-end="226">Open PhonePe, Google Pay, or Paytm.</p>
<p data-start="228" data-end="263">Choose <strong data-start="235" data-end="252">Pay to UPI ID</strong> and enter:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="265" data-end="291"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ybl</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="293" data-end="368">If your name appears and you can proceed to payment, your UPI ID is active.</p>
<p data-start="370" data-end="480">If it says <strong data-start="381" data-end="403">"UPI ID not found"</strong> or similar, then <strong data-start="421" data-end="446">the QR can never work</strong> until you use the correct UPI ID.</p>
<hr data-start="482" data-end="485">
<h3 data-section-id="z9rdsp" data-start="487" data-end="518">Step 2: If the UPI ID works</h3>
<p data-start="519" data-end="591">Update your QR generator to produce a standard UPI payment link such as:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="593" data-end="698"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl&amp;pn=Annand%20Sarma&amp;am=201&amp;cu=INR&amp;tn=Numero%20Annand%20AI%20Premium</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="700" data-end="746">Then regenerate <code data-start="716" data-end="732">payment_qr.png</code> and redeploy.</p>
<hr data-start="748" data-end="751">
<h3 data-section-id="1v46fb7" data-start="753" data-end="792">Step 3: If the UPI ID does not work</h3>
<p data-start="793" data-end="839">Find your actual UPI ID from your payment app.</p>
<p data-start="841" data-end="881">For example, it might be something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="883" data-end="953"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ibl
7099805039@okaxis
7099805039@axl
7099805039@upi</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="955" data-end="1025">Use <strong data-start="959" data-end="997">the exact UPI ID shown in your app</strong>, not just the phone number.</p>
<hr data-start="1027" data-end="1030">
<h2 data-section-id="bms1jc" data-start="1032" data-end="1074">I can help you finish this in 5 minutes</h2>
<p data-start="1076" data-end="1110">Please answer these two questions:</p>
<ol data-start="1112" data-end="1426">
<li data-section-id="vk9vkd" data-start="1112" data-end="1221">
<p data-start="1115" data-end="1160"><strong data-start="1115" data-end="1160">Which app is your UPI ID registered with?</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1164" data-end="1221">
<li data-section-id="tupqpt" data-start="1164" data-end="1173">
<p data-start="1166" data-end="1173">PhonePe</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jaet6x" data-start="1177" data-end="1189">
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1189">Google Pay</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1758509" data-start="1193" data-end="1200">
<p data-start="1195" data-end="1200">Paytm</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j42neu" data-start="1204" data-end="1210">
<p data-start="1206" data-end="1210">BHIM</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16uw1l8" data-start="1214" data-end="1221">
<p data-start="1216" data-end="1221">Other</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="aeooeg" data-start="1223" data-end="1426">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1296"><strong data-start="1226" data-end="1296">When you enter <code data-start="1243" data-end="1259">7099805039@ybl</code> manually in the app, what happens?</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1300" data-end="1426">
<li data-section-id="1koohuw" data-start="1300" data-end="1330">
<p data-start="1302" data-end="1330">✅ It shows <strong data-start="1313" data-end="1329">Annand Sarma</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="u3c4ul" data-start="1334" data-end="1367">
<p data-start="1336" data-end="1367">❌ It says <strong data-start="1346" data-end="1366">UPI ID not found</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n4wxor" data-start="1371" data-end="1426">
<p data-start="1373" data-end="1426">❌ It gives another error (tell me the exact message).</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1625" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Once I know those answers, I can tell you the exact fix. Right now, the evidence suggests the issue is more likely the <strong data-start="1547" data-end="1577">UPI ID or its registration</strong> than your Flask website or the QR image itself.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria