g xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-14" data-is-intersecting="true" style="--last-known-height: 92px;"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-14" data-turn-id-container="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-14" data-testid="conversation-turn-94" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="73395aff-0b24-4ed9-b540-e0870111c2c5" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="24">That explains the issue.</p>
<p data-start="26" data-end="212">The QR code itself is <strong data-start="48" data-end="57">valid</strong> (your ZXing decode proves that), but the <strong data-start="99" data-end="211">UPI app may reject it because the <code data-start="135" data-end="139">pn</code> (payee name) in the QR doesn't match the registered bank account name</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="214" data-end="256">Your QR currently contains something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="258" data-end="337"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>pa=7099805039@ybl
pn=ANANDA SARMAH
tn=Numero Annand AI Premium Purchase</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="339" data-end="450">If the bank account linked to <code data-start="369" data-end="385">7099805039@ybl</code> is registered as <strong data-start="403" data-end="420">Ananda Sarmah</strong>, then the safest approach is:</p>
<ul data-start="452" data-end="699">
<li data-section-id="1xas8sm" data-start="452" data-end="492">
<p data-start="454" data-end="492"><strong data-start="454" data-end="474">Payee Name (pn):</strong> <code data-start="475" data-end="490">Ananda Sarmah</code> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="t5bct7" data-start="493" data-end="586">
<p data-start="495" data-end="586"><strong data-start="495" data-end="519">Business/Brand Name:</strong> <code data-start="520" data-end="546">Numero Annand AI Premium</code> (in the payment note or on the website)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h2mvei" data-start="587" data-end="699">
<p data-start="589" data-end="699"><strong data-start="589" data-end="623">Numerology name "Annand Sarma"</strong> should be displayed in your website content, not inside the UPI payee name.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="701" data-end="713">For example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="715" data-end="817"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?
pa=7099805039@ybl
&amp;pn=Ananda%20Sarmah
&amp;tn=Numero%20Annand%20AI%20Premium%20Purchase</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="819" data-end="850">Your website can still display:</p>
<blockquote data-start="852" data-end="884">
<p data-start="854" data-end="884"><strong data-start="854" data-end="884">Numerology by Annand Sarma</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="886" data-end="904">while the QR uses:</p>
<blockquote data-start="906" data-end="933">
<p data-start="908" data-end="933"><strong data-start="908" data-end="933">Pay to: Ananda Sarmah</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="935" data-end="1056">This is normal. Many businesses use a brand name on their website while the bank account is under the owner's legal name.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="bub7f6" data-start="1058" data-end="1080">One important test</h3>
<p data-start="1082" data-end="1122">Open your PhonePe app and manually type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1124" data-end="1146"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ybl</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1148" data-end="1249">If PhonePe shows <strong data-start="1165" data-end="1182">Ananda Sarmah</strong> as the recipient, then your QR should also use <code data-start="1230" data-end="1248">pn=Ananda Sarmah</code>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="e871qo" data-start="1251" data-end="1284">If it still says "Invalid QR"</h3>
<p data-start="1286" data-end="1350">Then the problem is <strong data-start="1306" data-end="1322">not the name</strong>. It is likely one of these:</p>
<ol data-start="1352" data-end="1513">
<li data-section-id="1a8ok16" data-start="1352" data-end="1395">
<p data-start="1355" data-end="1395">The UPI ID <code data-start="1366" data-end="1382">7099805039@ybl</code> is inactive.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="49551i" data-start="1396" data-end="1462">
<p data-start="1399" data-end="1462">The QR image being served on your Vercel site is old or cached.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r77t2o" data-start="1463" data-end="1513">
<p data-start="1466" data-end="1513">The QR was generated with an incorrect UPI URI.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1708" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you can share the contents of your <code data-start="1553" data-end="1574">upi_qr_generator.py</code> file, I can check it line by line and provide the exact code needed to generate a fully compatible PhonePe, Google Pay, and Paytm QR.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidde