e solve</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-15" data-is-intersecting="true" style="--last-known-height: 92px;"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-15" data-turn-id-container="request-6a55a15d-ef98-83e8-a50e-64f23b4beb6b-15" data-testid="conversation-turn-96" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c5327dbe-109b-4ead-968c-34552a919ebb" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="63">The good news is that you've already identified the real cause.</p>
<p data-start="65" data-end="157">Your QR code <strong data-start="78" data-end="99">decodes correctly</strong>, which means the QR itself is valid. The decoded data is:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="159" data-end="284"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl
&amp;pn=ANANDA SARMAH
&amp;tn=Numero Annand AI Premium Purchase
&amp;mc=0000
&amp;mode=02
&amp;purpose=00</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="286" data-end="322">The problem is <strong data-start="301" data-end="321">not the QR image</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="324" data-end="367">The problem is the <strong data-start="343" data-end="366">payee name mismatch</strong>.</p>
<ul data-start="369" data-end="451">
<li data-section-id="1wujtjq" data-start="369" data-end="409">
<p data-start="371" data-end="409"><strong data-start="371" data-end="393">Bank account name:</strong> Ananda Sarmah ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p0c9jo" data-start="410" data-end="451">
<p data-start="412" data-end="451"><strong data-start="412" data-end="438">Brand/Numerology name:</strong> Annand Sarma</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="453" data-end="654">Many UPI apps (PhonePe, GPay, Paytm) compare the <code data-start="502" data-end="507">pn=</code> field with the registered bank account. If the names don't match closely enough, they may show <strong data-start="603" data-end="617">Invalid QR</strong>, <strong data-start="619" data-end="630">Bad URI</strong>, or refuse the payment.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="cw4pqx" data-start="656" data-end="683">Solution 1 (Recommended)</h2>
<p data-start="685" data-end="753">Generate the QR using the <strong data-start="711" data-end="732">bank account name</strong>, not the brand name.</p>
<p data-start="755" data-end="759">Use:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="761" data-end="871"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>UPI ID:
7099805039@ybl

Payee Name:
Ananda Sarmah

Transaction Note:
Numero Annand AI Premium Purchase</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="873" data-end="904">Then, on your website, display:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="906" data-end="942"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Consultation by
Annand Sarma</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="944" data-end="953">This way:</p>
<ul data-start="955" data-end="1027">
<li data-section-id="w4kle4" data-start="955" data-end="988">
<p data-start="957" data-end="988">QR uses the official bank name.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1btse3p" data-start="989" data-end="1027">
<p data-start="991" data-end="1027">Branding still shows "Annand Sarma".</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1029" data-end="1063">This is how most businesses do it.</p>
<hr data-start="1065" data-end="1068">
<h2 data-section-id="1jhsjgu" data-start="1070" data-end="1083">Solution 2</h2>
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1090">Keep:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1092" data-end="1116"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>pn=Ananda Sarmah</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1173">and put the business name only in the transaction note:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1175" data-end="1219"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>tn=Numero Annand AI Premium Purchase</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1221" data-end="1224">
<h2 data-section-id="16hhce0" data-start="1226" data-end="1239">Do NOT use</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1241" data-end="1264"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>pn=Annand Sarma</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1266" data-end="1302">if the bank account is registered as</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1304" data-end="1325"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Ananda Sarmah</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1327" data-end="1330">
<h2 data-section-id="w3vjpv" data-start="1332" data-end="1358">Final QR should contain</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1360" data-end="1465"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>upi://pay?pa=7099805039@ybl
&amp;pn=Ananda%20Sarmah
&amp;tn=Numero%20Annand%20AI%20Premium%20Purchase</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1467" data-end="1493">This is the safest format.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1nozk0b" data-start="1495" data-end="1513">One more thing</h3>
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1669">If it <strong data-start="1521" data-end="1592">still says "Invalid QR" even after changing <code data-start="1567" data-end="1571">pn</code> to <code data-start="1575" data-end="1590">Ananda Sarmah</code></strong>, then the issue is likely that <strong data-start="1624" data-end="1668"><code data-start="1626" data-end="1642">7099805039@ybl</code> is not an active UPI ID</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1671" data-end="1697">Please test this manually:</p>
<ol data-start="1699" data-end="1821">
<li data-section-id="vb36w9" data-start="1699" data-end="1715">
<p data-start="1702" data-end="1715">Open PhonePe.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12zqs1s" data-start="1716" data-end="1741">
<p data-start="1719" data-end="1741">Tap <strong data-start="1723" data-end="1740">Pay by UPI ID</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="k554jb" data-start="1742" data-end="1783">
<p data-start="1745" data-end="1751">Enter:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1755" data-end="1783"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>7099805039@ybl</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h1dnj5" data-start="1784" data-end="1821">
<p data-start="1787" data-end="1821">See if it shows <strong data-start="1803" data-end="1820">Ananda Sarmah</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1823" data-end="1938">If it says <strong data-start="1834" data-end="1856">"UPI ID not found"</strong> or <strong data-start="1860" data-end="1880">"Invalid UPI ID"</strong>, then the QR can never work until you use a valid UPI ID.</p>
<p data-start="1940" data-end="2009">Tell me <strong data-start="1948" data-end="2008">what happens when you search <code data-start="1979" data-end="1995">7099805039@ybl</code> in PhonePe</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2010" data-end="2082" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="b28a5x" data-start="2010" data-end="2043">
<p data-start="2012" data-end="2043">Does it show <strong data-start="2025" data-end="2042">Ananda Sarmah</strong>?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10w4qoz" data-start="2044" data-end="2082" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="2046" data-end="2082" data-is-last-node="">Or does it say <strong data-start="2061" data-end="2081">UPI ID not found</strong>?</p>
</li>
