<h3 data-section-id="fh0v9c" data-start="466" data-end="479">Important</h3>
<p data-start="480" data-end="666">Before deploying, <strong data-start="498" data-end="517">test the UPI ID</strong> <code data-start="518" data-end="534">7099805039@ybl</code> in PhonePe/GPay by entering it manually. If the app cannot find that UPI ID, no QR code will work until the UPI ID itself is valid.</p>
<p data-start="668" data-end="730">If you want, I can also <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">generate a <strong data-start="11" data-end="38" node="[object Object]" class="group-hover:entity-accent">professional branded QR</strong> with</span></span>:</p>
<ul data-start="731" data-end="931" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="lyf7sl" data-start="731" data-end="770">
<p data-start="733" data-end="770"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">"Scan &amp; Pay"</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wlg39x" data-start="771" data-end="810">
<p data-start="773" data-end="810"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">Your logo/title</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1etlrsl" data-start="811" data-end="850">
<p data-start="813" data-end="850"><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">₹201 / ₹501 automatically shown</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ra2p6u" data-start="851" data-end="931" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="853" data-end="931" data-is-last-node=""><span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">Better styling suitable for your website</span></span>. <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Coding Citation" class="rounded-xl px-1 text-token-text-secondary bg-token-bg-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-interactive-bg-secondary-selected"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-39f59a01.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></p>
