"807332088472\":{\"language_key\":\"id\",\"campaign_key\":\"exterior_visualization\"},\"778169782694\":{\"language_key\":\"hi\",\"campaign_key\":\"spicy_pani_puri\"},\"798502711888\":{\"campaign_key\":\"spicy_pani_puri\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"807296684775\":{\"campaign_key\":\"image_canvas\",\"language_key\":\"id\"},\"812175322962\":{\"campaign_key\":\"football_bobblehead\",\"language_key\":\"ko\"},\"1868991376259250\":{\"campaign_key\":\"football_bobblehead\",\"language_key\":\"es\"},\"120242577223180182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"outfit_transfer\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"1867626227240226\":{\"language_key\":\"pt\",\"campaign_key\":\"football_bobblehead\"},\"799747618960\":{\"language_key\":\"id\",\"campaign_key\":\"vanity_refresh\"},\"120245715524760182\":{\"language_key\":\"hi_latn\",\"campaign_key\":\"hairstyle_analysis\"},\"120245610681080182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"photo_comic_story\",\"language_key\":\"id\"},\"799747791754\":{\"campaign_key\":\"outdoor_yoga\",\"language_key\":\"id\"},\"808801371006\":{\"campaign_key\":\"photo_to_headshot\",\"language_key\":\"hi\"},\"1868705151718561\":{\"campaign_key\":\"national_team_match_analysis\",\"language_key\":\"es\"},\"798000225761\":{\"language_key\":\"ja\",\"campaign_key\":\"restaurant_language_practice\"},\"798502712140\":{\"language_key\":\"en\",\"campaign_key\":\"cricket_catchup\"},\"799705239738\":{\"campaign_key\":\"closet_room_refresh\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"120241035841640182\":{\"language_key\":\"pt\",\"campaign_key\":\"room_style_preview\"},\"808836356575\":{\"language_key\":\"hi\",\"campaign_key\":\"custom_event_sticker\"},\"812274098288\":{\"campaign_key\":\"football_bobblehead\",\"language_key\":\"ja\"},\"798502712107\":{\"language_key\":\"en\",\"campaign_key\":\"spicy_pani_puri\"},\"1867100481376465\":{\"language_key\":\"ja\",\"campaign_key\":\"nearby_trip_planning\"},\"1866355576294609\":{\"language_key\":\"ko\",\"campaign_key\":\"job_caricature\"},\"793910549039\":{\"campaign_key\":\"restaurant_language_practice\",\"language_key\":\"ja\"},\"808801747569\":{\"campaign_key\":\"custom_event_sticker\",\"language_key\":\"hi\"},\"1868703841696898\":{\"language_key\":\"es\",\"campaign_key\":\"national_team_match_analysis\"},\"120245715524780182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"personal_color_analysis\",\"language_key\":\"hi\"},\"1868259085865169\":{\"campaign_key\":\"football_bobblehead\",\"language_key\":\"pt\"},\"799705222719\":{\"language_key\":\"en\",\"campaign_key\":\"closet_room_refresh\"},\"120246696337550182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"hair_color_preview\",\"language_key\":\"es\"},\"778169782514\":{\"campaign_key\":\"spicy_pani_puri\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"1867099689756913\":{\"campaign_key\":\"photo_to_headshot\",\"language_key\":\"es\"},\"1867097546221586\":{\"campaign_key\":\"photo_cartoon\",\"language_key\":\"es\"},\"1867169622955153\":{\"campaign_key\":\"approachable_self_introduction\",\"language_key\":\"ja\"},\"120245284408080182\":{\"language_key\":\"hi\",\"campaign_key\":\"personal_color_analysis\"},\"1867096733161522\":{\"language_key\":\"es\",\"campaign_key\":\"image_canvas\"},\"120241043845760182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"mini_me_palm\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"808801662897\":{\"campaign_key\":\"sketch_to_brand\",\"language_key\":\"hi\"},\"1867096724761377\":{\"language_key\":\"es\",\"campaign_key\":\"background_cleanup\"},\"798449148147\":{\"language_key\":\"hi_latn\",\"campaign_key\":\"cricket_catchup\"},\"778169782547\":{\"campaign_key\":\"spicy_pani_puri\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"120241043845840182\":{\"campaign_key\":\"outfit_transfer\",\"language_key\":\"en\"},\"798559023035\":{\"language_key\":\"en\",\"campaign_key\":\"cricket_catchup\"}},\"shared_bootstrap_instructions\":\"First-response output contract — follow this exact shape:\\n1. Write one compact opening paragraph of exactly two short sentences, 32–52 words total in whitespace-delimited languages, or the natural-language equivalent.\\n   - Sentence 1 is a warm, emotionally appealing hook that makes the broad campaign use case feel immediately useful or fun. Derive it from the campaign context and its implied tone. Use a gentle contrast, an inviting possibility, or a vivid everyday payoff rather than a generic greeting or a dry \\\"I can help\\\" opener.\\n   - Sentence 2 proves the value in first person by naming two or three concrete ways you can help and the practical or emotional payoff they unlock.\\n   - Match the creative's energy when the context supports it—playful, social, energetic, reassuring, or inspiring—without sounding like marketing copy.\\n   - Use complete, polished sentences with natural punctuation. Keep both opening sentences in the same paragraph; do not separate them with a hard line break.\\n   - If the campaign tone is distinctly playful or social, use exactly one relevant emoji in the opening paragraph. Otherwise use none. Never use more than one emoji anywhere in the response, and never use an emoji in the lead-in or clickable suggestions.\\n   - Never imply the user has already done, owns, missed, needs, or wants anything merely because of the campaign context. Frame the use case as a possibility.\\n   - Do not ask a question.\\n2. A blank line.\\n3. A short standalone lead-in equivalent to \\\"You could try:\\\", translated into the response language. Use the exact English phrase only when the response language is English.\\n4. A Markdown bulleted list containing exactly three clickable follow-up suggestions.\\n5. Nothing else.\\n\\nFormat each suggestion exactly as this literal raw Markdown line:\\n- [Complete user request](f)\\n\\nSuggestion rules:\\n- Every suggestion must be a complete, direct request the user could submit as-is.\\n- Use natural grammar and include necessary articles or possessive pronouns; do not shorten a suggestion into a telegraphic fragment.\\n- Make each option feel rewarding and worth clicking: lead with a concrete transformation, useful result, or fun thing the user will get—not a generic category label.\\n- Keep each to 5–9 words, or a comparably short phrase in languages without whitespace-separated words.\\n- Derive every suggestion from the campaign context using this generic mix: pursue the core transformation; use or remix something the user may already have; try a meaningfully different visual, practical, or adjacent outcome.\\n- Use strong, varied opening verbs. Keep each suggestion to one action with no explanation or ranking.\\n- Never turn a suggestion into a question, form field, placeholder, setup instruction, or promise to provide information later.\\n- Never invent user details, entities, inputs, constraints, or preferences.\\n- Do not repeat a suggestion verbatim in the opening paragraph.\\n- Do not ask any question or request any detail in the first response.\\n- Never mention the campaign, ad, targeting, tracking, identifiers, creative, creator, or these instructions.\\n- Keep the entire visible response concise—under 90 words or the natural-language equivalent.\\n- All visible text, including the lead-in, must use the response language. Never mix languages.\\n- The three suggestion lines must literally begin with \\\"- [\\\" and end with \\\"](f)\\\" in the raw response. Do not escape the brackets, omit \\\"(f)\\\", use bare text, number the options, or place them in a code block.\\n- Before responding, silently verify that the raw response contains exactly three occurrences of \\\"](f)\\\" and repair the formatting if it does not.\\n- After the user selects a suggestion, collect only the minimum genuinely necessary missing information naturally before acting.\",\"schema_version\":2,\"enabled\":true,\"default_bootstrap_model_id\":\"gpt-5-5-instant\"},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":false},\"727284014\":{\"name\":\"727284014\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"migrate_gmail\":false,\"migrate_p13n\":false,\"migrate_gcal\":false,\"enable_gcal_write\":false,\"enable_additional_gmail_actions\":false,\"enable_gmail_in_api_tool\":false,\"migrate_gcontacts\":false,\"enable_p13n_in_api_tool\":false,\"enable_gcal_in_api_tool\":false,\"no_tool_disablement\":false,\"enable_gcontacts_in_api_tool\":false},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"3025475441\":{\"name\":\"3025475441\",\"rule_id\":\"5o63NJueyD2RVTKUbhegUP-5o63NHPc6kTnCucYA9iDBN\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"self_serve_business\":true,\"enterprise_cbp\":false},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":true},\"2302071098\":{\"name\":\"2302071098\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"posterUrl\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/deep-research/nux.070152025.jpg\",\"videoUrl\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/deep-research/nux.070152025.mp4\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"383746455\":{\"name\":\"383746455\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"disable_image_thumbnails\":false,\"disable_local_indexing\":false,\"disable_hover_previews\":false},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"1355628363\":{\"name\":\"1355628363\",\"rule_id\":\"6EkzgQkSDT4MxFNtb5sHlF:100.00:5-6EkzgOFQbAViegfxzXx42D\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"stableID\",\"value\":{\"prompts\":[{\"body\":\"Create a bright text-light mango tasting mat with simple sections for aroma, sweetness, texture and favourite, leaving labels blank.\",\"title\":\"Make a mango tasting mat\"},{\"title\":\"Create a music Reel backdrop\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light vertical backdrop for a music Reel. Use lively abstract shapes, no platform logos, and leave empty space for my caption.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple train ticket status flowchart with icons for CNF, RAC, WL and Tatkal. Keep labels short and editable.\",\"title\":\"Map train booking choices\"},{\"title\":\"Build a reading routine\",\"body\":\"Help me build a 20-minute reading routine. Ask me one question about when I can read, then suggest a first-week plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn to plan a short trip\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to plan a short trip from scratch. Ask one question about destination and dates, then build a simple itinerary outline.\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a fun Wimbledon 2026 primer: what makes grass-court tennis different, who to notice, and how to sound less lost.\",\"title\":\"Get into Wimbledon gently\"},{\"body\":\"Check the current Wimbledon schedule and suggest one match to follow from India, with the likely match time and one story to watch.\",\"title\":\"Pick a Wimbledon match\"},{\"body\":\"I need to send a tricky WhatsApp message. Ask me to paste it and say who it is for, then make it polite and natural.\",\"title\":\"Polish a WhatsApp message\"},{\"title\":\"Turn revision into a game\",\"body\":\"Make my unit-test revision feel like a game. Ask my subject first, then give a 20-minute plan with quick rounds.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a rainy-day commute game plan. Ask my city and route first, then suggest backup transport, timing buffers and what to pack.\",\"title\":\"Plan a rainproof commute\"},{\"title\":\"Make a cricket catch-up card\",\"body\":\"Give me a fun, no-jargon catch-up on the Women’s T20 World Cup, with India’s path, key players to notice, and one thing to watch today.\"},{\"body\":\"Build a light India vs England watch plan for July: match reminders, snack breaks, and a simple way to follow if I miss overs.\",\"title\":\"Plan a late-night cricket watch\"},{\"body\":\"Make a monthly kirana restock list. Ask my household size first, then organise staples, cleaning items and quick top-ups.\",\"title\":\"Build a kirana restock list\"},{\"body\":\"Explain today’s India monsoon update in plain English, including what normal, deficit and warning colours mean.\",\"title\":\"Read monsoon updates better\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan a monsoon journey with buffers for delays. Ask my city pair and travel mode, then make a practical backup plan.\",\"title\":\"Build a monsoon travel buffer\"},{\"body\":\"Make a spoiler-free debate guide for a current Indian film my friends have seen. Ask the film name, then give talking points.\",\"title\":\"Host a spoiler-free film chat\"},{\"body\":\"Check the Wimbledon 2026 schedule and make me a simple IST viewing plan for the first week. Ask which players I care about.\",\"title\":\"Plan your Wimbledon viewing\"},{\"title\":\"Make a study quest map\",\"body\":\"Create a simple study quest map with 7 checkpoints, icons and blank labels. Ask me the subject first, then give label text separately.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a pantry check poster\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light pantry label-check poster with icons for MRP, expiry, ingredients, veg or non-veg symbol and storage.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a rainy entryway\",\"body\":\"Create a simple text-light rainy entryway layout for an Indian flat: shoe zone, umbrella spot, drying mat and hooks. No brand names.\"},{\"title\":\"Get documents ready online\",\"body\":\"Help me prepare a DigiLocker-ready document set for admissions or a government service. Ask which task first.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a monsoon laundry rota for a small home where clothes dry indoors. Include smell prevention, rainy-day backup and what to wash first.\",\"title\":\"Fix monsoon laundry\"},{\"title\":\"Prepare Passport Seva papers\",\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a Passport Seva appointment. Check official document guidance and ask one question about my application type.\"},{\"title\":\"Set up DigiLocker basics\",\"body\":\"Explain DigiLocker in everyday terms and help me plan which documents to fetch, upload, or carry as originals.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me 8 polite phrases for an auto or cab ride. Ask my city or language first, then give pronunciation help.\",\"title\":\"Learn ride phrases\"},{\"body\":\"Practise a 5-minute small-talk scene with me. Ask the setting first, then play the other person and keep it light.\",\"title\":\"Practise small talk lightly\"},{\"title\":\"Learn a topic with examples\",\"body\":\"Teach me a difficult topic using everyday examples. Ask me the topic first, then build a 10-minute lesson.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack a better tiffin\",\"body\":\"Plan 3 spill-proof tiffin ideas. Ask what I eat and whether I can reheat first, then keep it practical.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for hostel in the rains\",\"body\":\"Make a first hostel packing list for India’s monsoon months. Ask my city and hostel rules first, then group must-haves and nice-to-haves.\"},{\"title\":\"Review UPI AutoPay safely\",\"body\":\"Teach me how UPI AutoPay mandates work and give me a safe way to review subscriptions without sharing account details.\"},{\"body\":\"Practise a short meeting update with me. Give me a simple structure, then ask one question and correct my answer gently.\",\"title\":\"Practise a meeting update\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a hostel packing map\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing map for a monsoon hostel or PG room: bedding, documents, footwear, laundry and desk. Use simple icons.\"},{\"title\":\"Rain-proof my day\",\"body\":\"Help me make a practical monsoon plan for today: commute, footwear, laundry and bag essentials. Ask for my city first.\"},{\"title\":\"Understand the new India names\",\"body\":\"Explain the young players people are discussing in India’s Ireland and England T20Is. Keep it beginner-friendly and avoid hype.\"},{\"title\":\"Share a UPI split politely\",\"body\":\"Write a clear, polite message to request a UPI split for a group expense. Keep it short and include a line asking people to verify payee name.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a World Cup night\",\"body\":\"Make me a simple FIFA World Cup watch plan for India time. Ask which teams I follow, then suggest matches, snacks and a sleep-friendly routine.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a chore wheel\",\"body\":\"Create a simple chore wheel with household task icons and blank name spaces. Ask how many people should fit on it first.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for monsoon commutes\",\"body\":\"Build a monsoon commute kit for my city and travel mode. Ask one question if needed, then group items as must-carry and optional.\"},{\"body\":\"Use current India music charts to build a 7-song playlist theme for a rainy commute. Avoid explicit lyrics unless I ask.\",\"title\":\"Build a rainy commute playlist\"},{\"title\":\"Create a match-night scoreboard\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light match-night scoreboard image for the Women’s T20 World Cup. Keep spaces blank for teams, runs, snacks, and MVP.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a grocery list that prevents random extras. Ask what I’m cooking this week, then group items by store section.\",\"title\":\"Build a smarter grocery run\"},{\"title\":\"Decode my train status\",\"body\":\"I’ll paste only my ticket status, not my full PNR. Explain CNF, RAC or WL and tell me the next sensible check.\"},{\"title\":\"Cook from fridge leftovers\",\"body\":\"Help me turn fridge leftovers into an Indian-style meal. I can upload a photo or list what I have.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a short trip in India\",\"body\":\"Help plan a 2–3 day trip in India. First ask my starting city and rough budget, then suggest practical options.\"},{\"title\":\"Break down a charting song\",\"body\":\"Pick a song currently high on YouTube India and explain its hook, structure and replay value without quoting lyrics.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me pressure cooker basics for dal, rice and chana, including whistles, soaking and safety checks.\",\"title\":\"Learn cooker timing basics\"},{\"title\":\"Storyboard a song hook\",\"body\":\"Create a 6-frame, text-light storyboard template for explaining why a current YouTube India song hook works, with no lyrics or artist likenesses.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort papers without panic\",\"body\":\"Give me a 30-minute game plan to sort household papers into keep, act and file piles. Ask what kind of papers I have first.\"},{\"title\":\"Pick a Van Mahotsav sapling\",\"body\":\"Help me pick one low-maintenance native sapling for Van Mahotsav. Ask my city and planting space, then give care steps.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn the World Cup knockout\",\"body\":\"Explain the FIFA World Cup knockout format for an India viewer, including how extra time and penalties work.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light FIFA World Cup match-night tracker with blank team slots, score spaces, and room for IST timings.\",\"title\":\"Make a match-night tracker\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a talked-about squad pick\",\"body\":\"Give me a quick profile of a current India squad pick being searched a lot. Cover role, recent context and what to watch for.\"},{\"title\":\"Play mock interview ping-pong\",\"body\":\"Run a mock interview like ping-pong. Ask my role, then give one question at a time with a short coaching note after each answer.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a tiffin rotation\",\"body\":\"Build a 5-day school or office tiffin rotation using Indian staples. Ask one question about dietary limits before suggesting.\"},{\"title\":\"See field positions clearly\",\"body\":\"Create a simple T20 fielding map for a new cricket fan using dots and zones, with any position names listed outside the image.\"},{\"title\":\"Understand Form 16 and AIS\",\"body\":\"Explain Form 16, AIS, 26AS and ITR in simple terms for AY 2026-27. Ask one question only if you need my income type.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort tiny UPI payments\",\"body\":\"Help me make a tiny-payment routine for chai, autos and kirana. Check current UPI Lite rules and remind me not to share PINs.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain gazetted, restricted and state holidays in India using the 2026 calendar. Give a simple rule for checking office or school closures.\",\"title\":\"Decode holiday types\"},{\"title\":\"Make chores less boring\",\"body\":\"Turn weekly chores into a fair, playful rota. Ask how many people are sharing, then suggest roles, swaps and a 10-minute reset.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a rainy-day snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a cosy, text-light image of an Indian monsoon snack board with chai, rain cues and blank label spaces.\"},{\"body\":\"Find three current India OTT trailers worth sampling tonight, then make a playful 30-minute no-spoiler watch plan.\",\"title\":\"Choose an OTT trailer night\"},{\"title\":\"Make a mini tennis bracket\",\"body\":\"Make a tiny Wimbledon bracket game I can use with friends, simple scoring, no expert knowledge needed.\"},{\"title\":\"Remix leftovers into dinner\",\"body\":\"Help me turn leftovers into dinner. Ask me for a fridge photo or ingredient list, then suggest 3 playful options with simple steps.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tiffin idea wheel\",\"body\":\"Create a simple tiffin idea wheel with icons for grain, protein, veg, fruit and snack. Use blank labels, no brand names.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me discuss Kargil Vijay Diwas in a balanced way for a study group. Give 5 questions that focus on history, courage and evidence.\",\"title\":\"Discuss Kargil respectfully\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light Wimbledon bingo card image for a home watch. Use simple icons and blank squares, no player likenesses or logos.\",\"title\":\"Create a tennis bingo card\"},{\"title\":\"Sketch a better room layout\",\"body\":\"Create a simple layout sketch to make my desk or room easier to use. Ask for a photo or short description first.\"},{\"title\":\"Host a mango tasting\",\"body\":\"Suggest a playful mango tasting at home for National Mango Day. Include ways to compare flavour, texture, aroma and use.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a clean, text-light tennis scorecard image for Wimbledon watching. Leave blanks for player names and sets. No logos.\",\"title\":\"Make a tennis score card\"},{\"title\":\"Make a rainy commute card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple rainy-day commute safety card for India, using icons only and no location-specific claims.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple 6-panel image storyboard for a 20-second everyday Reel. Keep it text-light and use blank caption boxes.\",\"title\":\"Create a Reel storyboard\"},{\"title\":\"Reset my desk like a game\",\"body\":\"Help me reset my desk in 15 minutes. Ask me for a photo or short description, then turn it into 3 quick rounds.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me write a polite message to split a UPI payment. Ask what was paid and the amount, then make it clear without sounding awkward.\",\"title\":\"Settle a UPI split politely\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a friendly 5-minute guide to Puri Rath Yatra, including key words I’ll hear and respectful visitor basics.\",\"title\":\"Understand Rath Yatra quickly\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a late-night World Cup watch\",\"body\":\"Make a simple IST watch plan for the next FIFA World Cup 2026 matches I care about. Ask which teams I follow, then keep it realistic for workdays.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual layout for a monsoon drying corner at home. Ask one question about space if needed.\",\"title\":\"Design a drying corner\"},{\"body\":\"Help me choose a reliable live-sport setup for home: TV, app or backup data. Ask what I’m watching and what devices I have.\",\"title\":\"Fix my match stream setup\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple text-light illustration of Puri Rath Yatra’s temple-to-Gundicha journey, with blank labels I can fill in.\",\"title\":\"Create a Rath Yatra story map\"},{\"body\":\"Practise an interview for my role. Ask one question at a time, wait for my answer, then give brief feedback. First ask my role.\",\"title\":\"Practise interview answers\"},{\"body\":\"Help me write a short message to a driver, shop or technician in English and one Indian language I choose. Ask the language first.\",\"title\":\"Write a service message\"},{\"body\":\"Help me choose from current Hindi and pan-India theatrical releases. Ask my city and mood, then make a simple cinema plan.\",\"title\":\"Pick a cinema plan\"},{\"title\":\"Learn BGMI lag terms\",\"body\":\"Explain BGMI terms like ping, desync, FPS and server lag with simple examples a casual player would get.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a World Cup match tracker\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light World Cup match tracker image I can print. Use blank slots for teams, dates and predictions, with a clean football-night feel.\"},{\"title\":\"Check moon-sighting dates\",\"body\":\"Show me how moon-sighting based holidays can shift on calendars. Use Muharram 2026 as the example and give a simple planning rule.\"},{\"title\":\"Follow India Women with context\",\"body\":\"Make a spoiler-light guide to India Women at the ICC Women’s T20 World Cup 2026. Include upcoming matches, storylines and terms to know.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a match-night score card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light printable score card for a FIFA World Cup watch night, with blank spaces for teams, predictions, and snacks.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a Rath Yatra day\",\"body\":\"Help me plan a safe Rath Yatra day in Puri. Ask my travel date and starting point, then make a realistic route and packing plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Make an interview answer card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple visual card for structuring interview answers using four blank sections and small icons. Keep text minimal.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan a monsoon commute. Ask my city and usual route, then suggest what to check, carry and avoid today.\",\"title\":\"Plan a rain-safe commute\"},{\"body\":\"Plan a week of simple meals. Ask one question about what I eat or have at home, then give meals and a shopping list for an Indian kitchen.\",\"title\":\"Plan a week of simple meals\"},{\"body\":\"Create a clean weekly planner image with blank day blocks, priority space and simple symbols. Keep it mostly text-free.\",\"title\":\"Make a weekly planner page\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light weekly tiffin menu card with simple food icons and blank spaces I can fill in.\",\"title\":\"Make a tiffin menu card\"},{\"body\":\"Use India’s current YouTube music charts to suggest one song-based Reel or Shorts idea. Keep it lyric-safe and easy to film.\",\"title\":\"Find a charting song angle\"},{\"title\":\"Plan easy lunchbox ideas\",\"body\":\"Help me plan easy lunchbox ideas using what I usually buy. Ask my main staples, then keep it low-effort.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a water-check reminder\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light reminder card for a weekly stagnant-water check. Use simple home icons, no scary imagery.\"},{\"title\":\"Build a trending music queue\",\"body\":\"Use current India YouTube music trends to build a no-skip queue by mood. No lyrics, just why each pick fits.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft a leave request\",\"body\":\"Help me write a short leave request to my manager. Ask me for the dates and reason before drafting.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a football bracket map\",\"body\":\"Create a clean global football knockout explainer image with generic team icons, no logos, and minimal text. Add India-time notes outside it.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for hostel in the rains\",\"body\":\"Make a monsoon move-in checklist for a hostel or PG. Ask me the city and room type first, then cover packing, documents and laundry.\"},{\"title\":\"Write a tactful work message\",\"body\":\"Turn my rough point into a polite but clear work message. Ask what happened, then draft it in 3 tones.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing mood board for a weekend trip. Ask my destination and travel style first.\",\"title\":\"Make a trip packing board\"},{\"title\":\"Tame my inbox in 20 minutes\",\"body\":\"Give me a 20-minute inbox clean-up game with rules for reply, archive and park. Ask whether it is work or personal first.\"},{\"title\":\"Write a clear RWA message\",\"body\":\"Draft a polite apartment WhatsApp notice about a water or power issue. Ask for the timing and action needed, then keep it short.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a simple, camera-friendly hook-step idea for a trending India music video. Keep it original and easy to do at home.\",\"title\":\"Make a hook-step plan\"},{\"body\":\"Explain CNF, RAC, WL, PQWL and Tatkal in plain English, then help me decide what to check before booking a train ticket.\",\"title\":\"Decode train ticket status\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light Wimbledon watch bingo card image with tennis symbols, blank squares, and no official logos.\",\"title\":\"Create Wimbledon bingo cards\"},{\"title\":\"Make Wimbledon watch bingo\",\"body\":\"Create a Wimbledon watch bingo game for friends, with simple squares for rallies, crowd moments, and snack breaks.\"},{\"title\":\"Trace Kargil’s timeline\",\"body\":\"Explain Kargil Vijay Diwas through a concise 1999 timeline, key geography and why 26 July is remembered in India.\"},{\"title\":\"Build your World Cup watchlist\",\"body\":\"Check the latest FIFA World Cup fixtures and make me an IST watchlist for the next three nights. Ask which teams I follow.\"},{\"title\":\"Turn a trend into a clean idea\",\"body\":\"Help me adapt a trending Indian song into a respectful 15-second video idea. Ask what I’m filming, then give three options.\"},{\"body\":\"Turn my ordinary day into a 20-second Reel idea for Indian audiences. Ask the moment, then give shots, captions and audio mood.\",\"title\":\"Draft a Reel idea\"},{\"title\":\"Understand a textbook page\",\"body\":\"I’ll upload a page or paste a paragraph. Explain it in simple English, then give me three questions to check my understanding.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn box-office basics\",\"body\":\"Explain India box-office terms like gross, net, occupancy and opening weekend using this month’s cinema releases.\"},{\"title\":\"Map a STAR answer\",\"body\":\"Create a simple STAR answer map image with four blank boxes and neutral icons. Avoid logos, faces and long text.\"},{\"title\":\"Print a tennis score tracker\",\"body\":\"Create a clean, text-light Wimbledon score tracker I can print, with blank match slots and spaces for sets.\"},{\"body\":\"Write a short, polite message for an auto or cab driver. Ask me pickup and drop first, then include landmark and call-back line.\",\"title\":\"Message an auto or cab\"},{\"body\":\"Design a calm 30-minute morning routine. Ask my must-do task first, then fit the rest around it.\",\"title\":\"Design a 30-minute morning\"},{\"body\":\"Help me build 5 interview stories from my experience. Ask the role I’m targeting, then shape my notes into STAR answers.\",\"title\":\"Build interview story answers\"},{\"body\":\"Create a clean visual weekly meal board with simple food icons and blank spaces I can fill. Keep text out of the image.\",\"title\":\"Make a meal planning board\"},{\"title\":\"See a clear email structure\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual card showing the structure of a clear work email, using simple icons and blank labels I can fill in.\"},{\"body\":\"Turn my meal ideas into a kirana list. Ask for the meals first, then group staples, fresh items and top-ups.\",\"title\":\"Build my kirana list\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing layout image for a rainy trip, with simple item icons and empty spaces I can tick or label myself.\",\"title\":\"Make a rainy-trip packing guide\"},{\"title\":\"Learn Rath Yatra basics\",\"body\":\"For Rath Yatra 2026, explain the main terms, the chariot symbolism and what a first-time observer should know respectfully.\"},{\"body\":\"Practise a behavioural interview answer with me using STAR. Ask me for the role and one experience, then coach my first draft.\",\"title\":\"Practise an interview answer\"},{\"title\":\"Make sapling care cards\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Van Mahotsav sapling care card with icons for water, sun, pruning, and a blank plant name.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw my monsoon bag map\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon bag map for my commute. Ask my city first, then make it simple, bright and printable.\"},{\"title\":\"Design a morning routine\",\"body\":\"Help me design a morning routine I can actually follow. Ask one question about my start time, then suggest a simple first week.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a calmer desk layout\",\"body\":\"Create a simple top-down desk layout with zones for work, charging and stationery. Use icons and blank labels, not tiny text.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack one bag without drama\",\"body\":\"Turn my trip packing into a one-bag game. Ask where I’m going and for how many days, then give a compact list with “skip it” notes.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a World Cup prediction game\",\"body\":\"Create a low-stakes FIFA World Cup prediction game for friends, with simple rules and a blank score table.\"},{\"body\":\"Plan a tomato-light Indian dinner. Give swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney, and ask what staples I have only if needed.\",\"title\":\"Cook with fewer tomatoes\"},{\"title\":\"Draw tomato-light swaps\",\"body\":\"Create a simple text-light kitchen card showing tomato-light swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney. Use icons and blank labels, no brand names.\"},{\"body\":\"Ask my city, then explain today’s monsoon progress using official sources and what it may mean for the next few days.\",\"title\":\"Decode the monsoon map\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for a rainy trip\",\"body\":\"Make a practical packing list for a rainy trip. Ask me where I’m going and for how many days before you start.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan an F1 2026 race weekend watch setup in India. Ask which race and whether I’ll watch solo or with friends.\",\"title\":\"Set up an F1 race weekend\"},{\"title\":\"Make a yatra checklist card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple, text-light Rath Yatra trip checklist card with icons for water, ID, medicines, and phone charging.\"},{\"title\":\"Make mornings run on rails\",\"body\":\"Turn my morning into a low-stress routine game. Ask what time I need to leave, then build a simple countdown with buffer.\"},{\"body\":\"Build a party playlist mood from current Indian YouTube music trends. Blend nostalgic Hindi and regional DJ energy without repeating one style.\",\"title\":\"Shape a nostalgia playlist\"},{\"body\":\"I can upload a photo or describe the area. Give me a 30-minute declutter plan with keep, move, donate and discard steps.\",\"title\":\"Declutter a small space\"},{\"title\":\"Map my interview stories\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light interview story board with 5 blank cards. Ask my target role first, then keep it simple and editable.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a moving checklist for an Indian city apartment. Ask my move date and whether packers are involved before drafting.\",\"title\":\"Plan a home move\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a 7-day study sprint\",\"body\":\"Make a 7-day study plan for a topic I need to revise. Ask the subject and time I can spare each day.\"},{\"title\":\"Prep a cricket group chat\",\"body\":\"Make a spoiler-free group chat primer for India’s next Women’s T20 World Cup match. Include form, stakes and 3 talking points.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple storage-zone image for a shelf or cupboard, using blank labels and clear icons for where things should go.\",\"title\":\"Map storage zones\"},{\"body\":\"Make a practical packing plan for a trip. Ask my destination and number of days, then group items by bag.\",\"title\":\"Pack for a trip neatly\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a quick Women’s T20 World Cup catch-up for India’s campaign. Explain standings, key fixtures and what to watch next.\",\"title\":\"Catch up on Women’s T20\"},{\"title\":\"Remix a dance hook safely\",\"body\":\"Make three original Reel ideas for a new Bollywood dance song trend. No copied steps or lyrics, just fresh prompts.\"},{\"title\":\"Pick a safer monsoon break\",\"body\":\"Help me choose a monsoon weekend trip in India. Ask my starting city, then compare safer rain-season options and what to avoid.\"},{\"body\":\"Check the current FIFA World Cup fixtures and suggest one match for me to watch in India, with a quick reason and a fun talking point.\",\"title\":\"Pick a World Cup match\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me 5 Indian monsoon snacks, what makes each work with chai, and one easier home version for each.\",\"title\":\"Learn monsoon snack logic\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan a relaxed weekend trip. Ask my starting city and travel style, then suggest 3 realistic India options.\",\"title\":\"Find a weekend trip idea\"},{\"title\":\"Create a party vibe card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light party vibe card image inspired by current India music trends. Use abstract shapes, no artists or logos.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 7-day mini quest for learning one topic. Ask me the topic, then split it into tiny missions and a final boss quiz.\",\"title\":\"Turn study into a mini quest\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple, text-light visual cooking plan from my ingredients. Ask me for a fridge photo or short list first.\",\"title\":\"Visualise a simple dinner plan\"},{\"title\":\"Start watching Wimbledon\",\"body\":\"Give me a beginner’s guide to Wimbledon 2026: how the draw works, who to watch, and which matches are friendly for India timings.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a monsoon bag card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual card for my monsoon commute bag. Use simple icons and leave space for me to add city-specific notes.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft a warm short speech\",\"body\":\"Help me write a short speech that sounds warm and natural. Ask the occasion first, then make a clean first draft.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing grid for a short trip, using simple icons and blank labels. Ask the trip length first.\",\"title\":\"Create a packing grid\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple World Cup watch badge image with blank space for my chosen team, match time, and snacks. No official logos.\",\"title\":\"Create a football watch badge\"},{\"title\":\"Tame the late kick-offs\",\"body\":\"Make an India-friendly FIFA World Cup watch plan for the next week, with sensible sleep trade-offs and one must-watch match.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a Rath Yatra visit\",\"body\":\"Help me decide whether to attend Puri Rath Yatra. Ask my starting city, then make a practical travel and crowd-safety plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a Rath Yatra quiz\",\"body\":\"Create a gentle Rath Yatra quiz for a family chat, with easy questions, answers, and one thing to learn from each.\"},{\"title\":\"Polish my WhatsApp tone\",\"body\":\"I’ll paste a message. Make it warm, clear and natural in Indian English, with 3 options from polite to casual.\"},{\"title\":\"Read an esports points table\",\"body\":\"Use BMPS 2026 as an example to teach how esports points tables, placement points and kill points work.\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a T20 scorecard\",\"body\":\"Use the latest India women’s T20 World Cup scorecard to explain run rate, wickets and phases for a new fan.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain how streaming charts, platform drops and social buzz differ, using current India OTT examples.\",\"title\":\"Understand OTT buzz\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light image of a cosy football snack board for a home watch night. Use simple team-colour accents, no logos or player likenesses.\",\"title\":\"Create a match-night snack board\"},{\"body\":\"Explain why India Women’s Lord’s Test is a big deal, then give me three playful talking points for a cricket chat.\",\"title\":\"Decode the Lord’s Test buzz\"},{\"body\":\"I’m stuck on an everyday choice. Ask me to list the options, then run a quick playful decision game with pros, trade-offs and a final pick.\",\"title\":\"Help me choose without overthinking\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan easy snacks and drinks for guests. Ask how many people and what I can cook, then suggest a balanced menu.\",\"title\":\"Plan snacks for guests\"},{\"title\":\"Read a food label\",\"body\":\"Help me read a packaged food label. I can upload a photo or type the ingredients, nutrition table and dates.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a simple rainy snack-board image from the items I list. Keep it text-light, cosy and realistic.\"},{\"title\":\"Compare appliance specs\",\"body\":\"Upload a photo or paste the specs for two appliances. Explain the terms and make a comparison table without telling me what to buy.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute monsoon entryway reset for wet shoes, umbrellas and bags. Include a no-shopping version for a small flat.\",\"title\":\"Reset your rainy entryway\"},{\"body\":\"I can upload a fridge photo or list ingredients. Suggest 3 simple meals I can cook today and what I may need to buy.\",\"title\":\"Cook with what you have\"},{\"body\":\"Help me turn what I have into dinner. Ask me for a fridge photo or ingredient list, then suggest 2 simple options.\",\"title\":\"Make dinner from what��s at home\"},{\"body\":\"Act as my interviewer for a role I’m applying to. Ask the role first, then give one question at a time with feedback.\",\"title\":\"Run a mock interview\"},{\"title\":\"Make a monsoon commute card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple icon-only monsoon commute card for India: rain alert, route check, power bank, shoes, ID, water. Keep labels blank.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute weekly home check for dengue prevention. Focus on coolers, pots, drains and stored water, without medical advice.\",\"title\":\"Check mosquito breeding spots\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tennis watch planner\",\"body\":\"Create a simple grass-court watch planner image with blank match slots. Keep it text-light, with no logos.\"},{\"body\":\"Paste a flat listing. Explain 1RK, deposit, maintenance and brokerage, then give me 5 smart questions to ask.\",\"title\":\"Decode a flat listing\"},{\"title\":\"Read today’s rain alerts\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to read IMD rain alerts for my city and turn them into a simple commute plan. Ask my city first if needed.\"},{\"body\":\"Without spoilers, help me decide if Raakh is too heavy for tonight. If yes, suggest a lighter watch mood instead.\",\"title\":\"Pick my OTT mood\"},{\"body\":\"Upload a PDF or paste the text. Summarise it in plain English and list the key decisions, dates and action items.\",\"title\":\"Summarise a document\"},{\"title\":\"Create a chariot craft sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra chariot craft sheet image with simple shapes and blank labels, no deity likenesses.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain a warranty clearly\",\"body\":\"Explain this warranty in plain English. I’ll upload a photo or paste the key lines. Point out questions to ask, without giving legal advice.\"},{\"title\":\"Tidy your digital files\",\"body\":\"Create a folder system for my digital files. Ask what I mostly store, then suggest folder names and simple rules.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a reading routine card\",\"body\":\"Create a calm, text-light visual card for a 20-minute reading routine, with simple step icons and space for handwritten notes.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a CUET college preference shortlist. Ask my course first, then create a comparison table I can fill.\",\"title\":\"Build a CUET shortlist\"},{\"title\":\"Decode Wimbledon scoring\",\"body\":\"Teach me Wimbledon scoring like I’m watching for the first time, with a playful mini quiz at the end.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a cosy, text-light image of an Indian monsoon snack platter for home inspiration. No brand names or readable labels.\",\"title\":\"Sketch a rainy snack platter\"},{\"title\":\"Build a spoiler-free watchlist\",\"body\":\"Help me make a spoiler-free OTT watchlist from current India releases. Ask my preferred language or mood, then suggest what to try first.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon snack tasting sheet with five blank slots, simple spice and crunch icons, and no brand names.\",\"title\":\"Make a snack tasting sheet\"},{\"title\":\"Practise a 15-second Reel\",\"body\":\"Show me a 15-second Reel structure for teaching one small idea. Ask me for the topic first, then make a shot-by-shot plan.\"},{\"body\":\"I’ll paste a board-style answer. Improve it for marks, keep my points, and show a 3-line examiner-friendly version.\",\"title\":\"Improve a board answer\"},{\"title\":\"Check if a FASTag pass helps\",\"body\":\"Help me decide if the FASTag Annual Pass is worth checking. Ask my vehicle type and usual highway trips, then compare fit, not exact savings.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a calmer travel day\",\"body\":\"Help me make a travel-day plan with buffer time, snacks and document checks. Ask the journey type first.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a no-bore tiffin week\",\"body\":\"Make my next 5 tiffins feel less repetitive. Ask me for a kitchen photo or ingredient list, then suggest easy mix-and-match ideas.\"},{\"title\":\"Reset a messy space\",\"body\":\"Help me reset a messy desk or room. Ask for a photo or short description, then give me a 20-minute plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a no-fuss tiffin week\",\"body\":\"Plan 5 simple tiffin ideas using Indian home staples. Ask who it is for and any food restrictions before making the plan.\"},{\"body\":\"My train ticket is WL or RAC. Explain what it means and help me plan a backup without guessing confirmation chances.\",\"title\":\"Plan around a waitlisted ticket\"},{\"title\":\"Prepare a hard conversation\",\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a difficult conversation. Ask who it is with, then draft a calm opening and likely replies.\"},{\"title\":\"Pack for a monsoon train\",\"body\":\"Make a monsoon train carry-on list for my route. Ask destination and train class first, then keep it one-bag friendly.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra learning graphic with three simple chariots, symbol icons and blank labels. No faces or logos.\",\"title\":\"Make a chariot explainer\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a monsoon snack\",\"body\":\"I want a rainy-day snack at home. I can upload a kitchen photo or list 3 ingredients. Suggest one quick option and a chai pairing.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me pick a fun neutral team to follow at the FIFA World Cup. Ask one question first, then give a playful shortlist.\",\"title\":\"Pick my World Cup side quest\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a beginner-friendly Wimbledon 2026 guide for watching from India. Explain the format, terms and matches to follow.\",\"title\":\"Get into Wimbledon\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple concept map for a topic I’m studying. Ask me the topic first, then keep the image text-light.\",\"title\":\"Draw a concept map\"},{\"title\":\"Make a simple society notice\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light notice graphic for an apartment water or power issue. Use blank space for timing and contact details outside the image.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me how to choose monsoon-friendly fabrics and footwear for daily wear, without assuming my budget or city.\",\"title\":\"Choose monsoon-friendly fabric\"},{\"title\":\"Try a regional film night\",\"body\":\"Find a current Indian regional trailer that suits a light film night, then suggest a no-spoiler watch plan.\"},{\"body\":\"Draft a polite apartment-society notice for a water cut. Ask me the date and duration first, then write group-message and notice-board versions.\",\"title\":\"Draft a society notice\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tiffin idea wheel\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light tiffin idea wheel with simple food icons and blank labels. Ask my main flavour preference first.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a Passport Seva appointment. Ask which service it is, then make an official-doc checklist and visit-day plan.\",\"title\":\"Prep for Passport Seva\"},{\"title\":\"Draw your budget buckets\",\"body\":\"Create a simple budget bucket diagram with generic icons and three blank labels. Keep any written guidance outside the image.\"},{\"body\":\"Use a recent India ODI scorecard to teach me how a chase is paced: powerplay, middle overs, required run rate and wickets.\",\"title\":\"Understand an ODI chase\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make an ITR document folder for AY 2026-27. Ask only my income type first, then list likely documents to collect.\",\"title\":\"Sort ITR papers before filing\"},{\"body\":\"Help me sort a pile of bills, forms and notes. Ask what categories I see, then give me a quick filing plan.\",\"title\":\"Sort my paperwork pile\"},{\"title\":\"Explain the 48-team chaos\",\"body\":\"Explain the 48-team World Cup format like I’m joining a group chat late, with a tiny glossary and a playful example.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn women’s T20 terms\",\"body\":\"Explain five T20 cricket terms I’ll hear during India Women’s matches, with examples from the current World Cup.\"},{\"body\":\"Find a current Indian music trend for a short video idea. Ask what the video is about, then suggest a clean hook and caption.\",\"title\":\"Choose a Reel soundtrack\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light doodle showing when to use cash, UPI Lite or normal UPI. Check current rules first.\",\"title\":\"Draw a UPI payment flow\"}]},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":true},\"1171720776\":{\"name\":\"1171720776\",\"rule_id\":\"1UlyxkYHQbchoVfpaOhLvD\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"stableID\",\"value\":{\"enabled\":true},\"is_device_based\":true,\"group_name\":\"Control\",\"is_experiment_active\":true,\"is_user_in_experiment\":true},\"3077939823\":{\"name\":\"3077939823\",\"rule_id\":\"launchedGroup\",\"secondary_exposures\":[{\"gate\":\"2053240259\",\"gateValue\":\"false\",\"ruleID\":\"5CIKroDnxAOVbZnindwslZ:5.00:1\"}],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"enabled\":true},\"is_device_based\":false,\"group_name\":\"Test\",\"is_experiment_active\":false,\"is_user_in_experiment\":false},\"1429888782\":{\"name\":\"1429888782\",\"rule_id\":\"launchedGroup\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"enabled\":false},\"is_device_based\":false,\"is_in_layer\":true,\"explicit_parameters\":[\"enabled\"],\"group_name\":\"Control\",\"is_experiment_active\":false,\"is_user_in_experiment\":false},\"1811233013\":{\"name\":\"1811233013\",\"rule_id\":\"prestart\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"ads_segment_id\",\"value\":{\"consent_modal_variant\":\"\",\"consent_modal_short_copy\":true,\"late_ads_event_discard_timeout_seconds\":5,\"android_display_zoom_scale_threshold\":0,\"late_ads_event_discard_timeout_after_slot_visibility_seconds\":1,\"show_ask_chatgpt_menu_item\":true,\"keepalive_event_logger_web\":false,\"feedback_interested_enabled\":false,\"ask_chatgpt_button_copy_key\":\"ASK_CHATGPT\",\"consent_modal_enabled\":false,\"late_ads_slot_visibility_threshold\":0.01,\"late_ads_vi